<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TVM5.1.10">
<l>āṉā ṉāḷuṭaiyāṉeṉṟaḵtēkoṇ ṭukantuvantu</l>
<l>tāṉē yiṉṉaruḷceyteṉṉaimuṟṟavun tāṉāṉāṉ</l>
<l>mīṉā yāmaiyumāy naraciṅkamu māykkuṟaḷāy</l>
<l>kāṉā reṉāmumāyk kaṟkiyāmiṉṉaṅ kārvaṇṇaṉē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Taking in that: that he was one who possesses a servant, he rejoiced, came</l>
<l>himself [and] did sweet grace [and] he totally became me,</l>
<l>the one with cloud colour who moreover is fish, tortoise, man-lion,</l>
<l>dwarf, a boar roaring in the forest [and] Kalki.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
